!! 异 ^
>` 相同为0，不同为1`
> 交换两个数的值





* `A ^ 0 = A`
|A|0000 |1111|
|B|0000|0000|
|C|0000|1111|

* `A ^ A = 0`
|A|0000 |1111|
|B|0000|1111|
|C|0000|0000|

* `A ^ B ^ A = B`

```python
a = 2
b = 5
a = a ^ b
b = b ^ a
# b = b ^  a ^ b
# b = a
a = a ^ b
# a = a ^ b ^ a
# a = b
```